Subtract two sparse_numeric vectors

sparse_sub.Rd

Computes the elementwise difference of two sparse_numeric vectors that have the same length.

Usage

sparse_sub(x, y)

# S4 method for class 'sparse_numeric,sparse_numeric'
sparse_sub(x, y)

Arguments

x, y

Objects of class sparse_numeric.

Value

A sparse_numeric object representing x - y.
